Package mech.mania.engine.server.api

Class GameStateController

  • java.lang.Object
    • mech.mania.engine.server.api.GameStateController
  • public class GameStateController
extends java.lang.Object
    An API for getting information from the game state. Will handle storing GameState, VisualizerTurns, and any other objects that need storing throughout.
